                <h3 class="card-title">African American Civil War Memorial</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>Over 200,000 African-American soldiers and sailors served in the U.S. Army and Navy during the Civil War. Their service helped to end the war and free over four million slaves. The African American Civil War Memorial honors their service and sacrifice.</p>
